TY  - JOUR
TI  - How to Control Controlled School Choice: Comment
AU  - Doğan, Battal
AB  - [Echenique and Yenmez (2015), in Theorem 2, characterize choice rules that are "generated by reserves for the priority." We show that the "only if" part is not correct. We exhibit a choice rule that is generated by reserves for the priority but violates one of their axioms. We reformulate the axiom and repair the result.]
